Type of Feat: Epic
Prerequisites: 21st level, Eldritch Blast 8d6, Spellcraft 24.
Specifics: The character's eldritch blasts deal +50% damage and have +2 to attack rolls. In addition, the area of effect is doubled for Eldritch Chain, Eldritch Doom, and Eldritch Cone. Eldritch Doom affects all targets within 40', for eldritch chain the distance between targets increases to 60', and for eldritch cone the length expands to 60'.
Use: Automatic.